────────────────────────────
5. Mandatory Prior Notice
────────────────────────────
Before modifying, forking, or redistributing the Software,
you MUST notify the Wista Project in advance.

The notice must include:
- Name of the individual or organization
- Description of intended use or modifications
- Planned public URL, if applicable

Notification must be sent via one of the following:
- GitHub Issue (https://github.com/wista-project)
- Email: wista-project@outlook.jp

Any modification or redistribution performed without prior notice
